Package musichub.business

Class Chanson

  • java.lang.Object
    • musichub.business.Element
      • musichub.business.Chanson
  • public class Chanson
extends Element
    Chanson is a song object in the librairy.

    A song can be added and removed from the librairy, an Album or a Playlist object.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    FERNANDES Mickael and LECLERC Maxence
    See Also:
    Element, ElementList, Album, Playlist
